    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants its pristine designation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning collector who demands mechanical and aesthetic excellence without exception.",
