      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 981-generation Porsche Cayman S represents the pinnacle of mid-engine balance. Powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six, the powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. This example features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and the Sport Chrono package, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and optimized damping. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the chassis remains stiff and the paint depth is consistent with a factory finish. No over-rev events on the DME report; this is a true collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
